body:
In regressions of cases from the SystemVerilog LRM, legal case on 1800-2012 page 664 (or 1800-2023 page 732) errors out:

%Error: syntax error, unexpected '{', expecting '['
    | module complex_ports ( {c,d}, .e(f) );
    |                     ^
%Error: syntax error, unexpected '.', expecting '['
    | module same_port (.a(i), .b(i));
    |                 ^

**Code:**
```
module complex_ports ( {c,d}, .e(f) );
  input signed [7:0] c;
  input signed [7:0] d;
  output [7:0] f;
endmodule

module same_port (.a(i), .b(i));
  input [7:0] i;
endmodule
```

**Version:**
5.044

**Environment:**
Centos 7.9，GCC 11.5

